Criteria for Selecting Blocks Recommended for Production Code

Blocks in Simulink that are designed for plant modeling and/or rapid prototyping
 environments may not be suitable for production code deployment. A block is not
 suitable for production deployment when the generated code:
Depends on continuous time
References non-finite values (Inf, -Inf, and NaN)
Contains instrumentation code suitable only for rapid prototyping
